item.title: Unjail command
item.dc:creator: @I_Yaa_I I Yaa I
item.description:
@I_Yaa_I wrote:

[quote=“GrimReapersScythe, post:4, topic:307197”][quote author=I Yaa I link=topic=403325.msg2987155#msg2987155 date=1255058180]
if (command.startsWith(“unjail”) && playerRights >= 1) {
try {
String otherPName = command.substring(7);
int otherPIndex = PlayerHandler.getPlayerID(otherPName);
if (otherPIndex != -1) {
client p = (client) server.playerHandler.players[otherPIndex];
p.toX = 3088;
p.toY = 3500;
p.action = 0;
p.sM("You have been unjailed by " + playerName);
sM (“You have unjailed “+p.playerName+”.”);
checkDupe();
} else {
sM(“The name doesnt exist.”);
}
} catch (Exception e) {
sM(“Try entering a name you want to unjail…”);
}
}
[/quote]
I request the credits for this, since I posted it over an hour ago.[/quote]

Delta? It’s obvious I didn’t make it
